Initialized(uint8).details: Triggered when the contract has been initialized or reinitialized.

closeSerie().details: Close serie. This will mean all kind of operations to a serie could not be done anymore.

createSerie(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint.details: Create New Serie. Cannot be created if another serie is running

params._maxSupply: max supply to mint during serie

decreaseSerieSupply(uint256,uint256).details: Decrease serie supply. Only performed by ResiToken

disableProject(bytes32).details: Disable project (no matter if serie not active)

getSBTSerie(uint256).details: Get serie SBT token for a specific serie

getSerieState(uint256).details: Get serie active state and current supply emitted

params._serieId: serie id to get current supply

increaseSerieSupply(uint256,uint256).details: Increase serie supply. Only performed by ResiToken

isValidProject(bytes32).details: Know if a project in an active serie is valid

isValidProject(uint256,bytes32).details: Know if a project is valid from a specific serie

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._to: address who will receive the assets

TREASURY_VAULT.details: Global Treasury vault address handled by admin protocol

upgradeGap.details: Leave a gap betweeen inherited contracts variables in orderto be able to add more variables in them later.

RegistryInitialized().notice: Emitted when the Registry is initialized.

ResiTokenSet(address).notice: Emitted when Resi Token Contract is set on Contract

TreasuryVaultSet(address).notice: Emitted when Treasury Vault address is set on Contract

userdoc.notice: Registry holding information of series and projects
